{"tid":877336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「Android之父」被爆強逼員工口交　谷歌9千萬美元封鎖消息","createTime":"2018-10-26T09:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T10:01:46.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f36a4c8ee549663292c607d6b593e6d9d396f9","tid":877336,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"2018-10-26 15:30:44<br />\n搜尋龍頭谷歌（ Google ）近年因公司性騷擾醜聞形象蒙塵，即便對外稱已有 48 名員工因此遭解雇，卻仍被知情人士爆料，有「安卓系統之父」美譽的安迪‧魯賓（ Andy Rubin ），曾逼迫女同事口交，事後他雖然離開 Google ，卻拿到高達 9 千萬美元（約 28 億元新台幣）的解雇金。<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約時報》報導，成功研發「安卓作業系統」的安迪‧魯賓，被人檢舉曾在辦公室對女員工提出口交要求，資安人員還在其個人電腦發現不雅影片，但離職前他仍拿到天價解雇金。一名 Google 前資深工程師透露，除了魯賓外，有兩位公司高層也是相同情況，事件都被 Google 給壓了下來。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 過去曾對外表示，近兩年有 48 名員工因涉及性騷擾遭到解雇，其中包括 13 名高階主管。對於《紐約時報》指控， Google 僅回應未來會極力防範性騷擾事件再發生，對於解雇金部分， Google 則重申不會給因性騷擾離職的員工一毛錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1540533984-3cf05f34acb800e38d5d2a47bb8224f9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1540533984-3cf05f34acb800e38d5d2a47bb8224f9.png&h=c81dd996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「安卓之父」安迪‧魯賓。（圖／翻攝推特）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20181026/3034721/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20181026%2F3034721%2F&d=pBvlUjHteML23fzRuHOJCgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=f5a7169f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20181026/3034721/</a>"},{"pid":"387c04539ac3f0fc351a7e3a3ce46a27d97d3dbc","tid":877336,"uid":49812,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:25:07.000Z","msg":"#metoo<br />\n又發難喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa07c58759f1371742bb45777736846d36f2c960","tid":87